t-and-scripts: Top-level project files — CLAUDE.md project overview, PowerShell recovery script, commands reference, version marker, and git configuration.\n\n## Instructions\n\nAnalyze all files matching your area's patterns. Return a JSON report with `area`, `files`, `area_summary`, `cross_area_refs`, and optionally `suggested_splits`."
