    "content": "## Area: core-application\n**Project:** Guanine(CodeEdit)\n**Date:** 2026-04-06\n\n## Explorer Report\n\n```json\n{\n  \"area\": \"core-application\",\n  \"files\": [\n    {\n      \"path\": \"file_merger.py\",\n      \"role\": \"entry-point\",\n      \"exports\": [\n        \"FileVersion(source_name, source_root, absolute_path, relative_path, file_size, modified_time, created_time, sha256, line_count, is_binary) -> dataclass\",\n        \"MergeItem(relative_path, versions, category, selected_index, resolved) -> dataclass\",\n        \"SourceConfig(name, path, priority) -> dataclass\",\n        \"FileScanner(ignore_patterns) -> class\",\n        \"MergeEngine() -> class\",\n        \"RecoveryAdvisor() -> class\",\n        \"EditorHistoryExtractor(project_folder, progress_queue) -> class\",\n        \"generate_side_by_side_diff(version_a, version_b, context_lines) -> list\",\n        \"list_sessions() -> list\",\n        \"get_active_session_id() -> str\",\n        \"set_active_session(session_id) -> None\",\n        \"save_session_meta(session_id, session_name) -> None\",\n        \"save_config(sources, target_dir, ignore_patterns) -> None\",\n        \"load_config(session_id) -> dict\",\n        \"save_inventory_state(inventory) -> None\",\n        \"save_item_resolution(relative_path, selected_index, resolved) -> None\",\n        \"save_batch_resolutions(updates) -> None\",\n        \"load_inventory_state(session_id) -> dict\",\n        \"delete_session(session_id) -> None\",\n        \"app -> Flask application instance\",\n        \"state -> dict (global application state)\"\n      ],\n      \"imports_from\": [\n        \"os (stdlib)\",\n        \"sys (stdlib)\",\n        \"hashlib (stdlib)\",\n        \"json (stdlib)\",\n        \"difflib (stdlib)\",\n        \"threading (stdlib)\",\n        \"fnmatch (stdlib)\",\n        \"shutil (stdlib)\",\n        \"time (stdlib)\",\n        \"queue (stdlib)\",\n        \"re (stdlib)\",\n        \"sqlite3 (st