ce layer for SQLite databases. Together these files establish project identity, operational boundaries, and multi-modal access (web UI vs CLI) to the file recovery functionality.\",\n  \"cross_area_refs\": [\n    \"restore_deleted_files.ps1 references EditorHistoryExtractor logic from core-application (file_merger.py)\",\n    \"CLAUDE.md documents FileScanner, MergeEngine, EditorHistoryExtractor classes from core-application\",\n    \"CLAUDE.md references templates/ directory from web-templates area\",\n    \"sessions/ directory is used by SQLite persistence layer in core-application (file_merger.py)\",\n    \"CLAUDE.md references .claude/rules/ from claude-config-and-rules area\",\n    \"CLAUDE.md references agentic/ documentation from agentic-docs-and-workflows area\"\n  ],\n  \"suggested_splits\": []\n}\n```\n\n## Relationship Edges for This Area\n\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"core-application\",\n    \"to_area\": \"project-root-and-scripts\",\n    \"type\": \"calls\",\n    \"details\": \"file_merger.py writes SQLite databases to the sessions/ directory for persistence\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"project-root-and-scripts\",\n    \"to_area\": \"core-application\",\n    \"type\": \"shares_types\",\n    \"details\": \"restore_deleted_files.ps1 reimplements EditorHistoryExtractor logic from file_merger.py; CLAUDE.md documents FileScanner, MergeEngine, EditorHistoryExtractor classes\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"project-root-and-scripts\",\n    \"to_area\": \"web-templates\",\n    \"type\": \"configures\",\n    \"details\": \"CLAUDE.md references templates/ directory as part of project layout documentation\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"project-root-and-scripts\",\n    \"to_area\": \"claude-config-and-rules\",\n    \"type\": \"configures\",\n    \"details\": \"CLAUDE.md references .claude/rules/ as part of the rule discovery protocol\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"project-root-and-scripts\",\n    \"to_area\": \"agentic-docs-and-workflows\",\n    \"type\": \"configures\",\n    \"details\": \"CLAUDE.md references agentic/ documentation as part of the project documentation index\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n## Repo Analysis (AST-based)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"repo\": \"local/Guanine(CodeEdit)-9b8e0840\",\n  \"indexed_at\": \"2026-04-06T16:32:22.900574\",\n  \"file_count\": 39,\n  \"symbol_count\": 519,\n  \"languages\": {\n    \"python\": 39\n  },\n  \"directories\": {\n    \".code-index/\": 26,\n    \"agentic/\": 12,\n    \"(root)\": 1\n  },\n  \"symbol_kinds\": {\n    \"function\": 297,\n    \"method\": 147,\n    \"constant\": 45,\n    \"class\": 30\n  },\n  \"most_central_symbols\": [\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/engine/knowledge.py::resolve_knowledge#function\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"function\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/engine/loop.py::process_agentic_loop#function\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"function\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/engine/openrouter.py::OpenRouterClient#class\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"class\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/engine/runner.py::LightweightWorkflowSession#class\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"class\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/engine/tool_executor.py::execute_tool_call#function\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"function\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/tools/get_fil