ameters\",\n        \"multi-source history scanning\",\n        \"dry-run mode\",\n        \"progress reporting with colorized output\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Standalone PowerShell script for recovering deleted files from editor local history (Windsurf, VS Code, Cursor) without requiring the web UI; supports dry-run, force overwrite, exclude filters, and cross-editor history path detection.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"0.12.0\",\n      \"role\": \"asset\",\n      \"exports\": [],\n      \"imports_from\": [],\n      \"key_functions\": [],\n      \"patterns\": [],\n      \"summary\": \"Version marker file containing pip output artifact indicating pathspec package version 1.0.4 is installed.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \".gitignore\",\n      \"role\": \"config\",\n      \"exports\": [],\n      \"imports_from\": [],\n      \"key_functions\": [],\n      \"patterns\": [\n        \"git configuration\",\n        \"runtime data exclusion\",\n        \"Python cache exclusion\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Git ignore rules excluding sessions directory, merger config/state files, merge logs, and Python cache files.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"sessions/\",\n      \"role\": \"utility\",\n      \"exports\": [],\n      \"imports_from\": [],\n      \"key_functions\": [],\n      \"patterns\": [\n        \"runtime data storage\",\n        \"SQLite database directory\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Empty runtime directory for per-session SQLite database files used by the Flask application for persistence.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"area_summary\": \"This area serves as the project's entry point and operational metadata layer. CLAUDE.md acts as the central discovery hub for AI agents, implementing a decentralized documentation protocol that directs agents to module-specific RULES_INDEX.md files. The PowerShell script provides a standalone command-line alternative to the web UI for file recovery operations. The sessions/ directory acts as the runtime persistence layer for SQLite databases. Together these files establish project identity, operational boundaries, and multi-modal access (web UI vs CLI) to the file recovery functionality.\",\n  \"cross_area_refs\": [\n    \"restore_deleted_files.ps1 references EditorHistoryExtractor logic from core-application (file_merger.py)\",\n    \"CLAUDE.md documents FileScanner, MergeEngine, EditorHistoryExtractor classes from core-application\",\n    \"CLAUDE.md references templates/ directory from web-templates area\",\n    \"sessions/ directory is used by SQLite persistence layer in core-application (file_merger.py)\",\n    \"CLAUDE.md references .claude/rules/ from claude-config-and-rules area\",\n    \"CLAUDE.md references agentic/ documentation from agentic-docs-and-workflows area\"\n  ],\n  \"suggested_splits\": []\n}\n```\n\n## Relationship Edges for This Area\n\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"core-application\",\n    \"to_area\": \"project-root-and-scripts\",\n    \"type\": \"calls\",\n    \"details\": \"file_merger.py writes SQLite databases to the sessions/ directory for persistence\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"project-root-and-scripts\",\n    \"to_area\": \"core-application\",\n    \"type\": \"shares_types\",\n    \"details\": \"restore_deleted_files.ps1 reimplements EditorHistoryExtractor logic from file_merger.py; CLAUDE.md documents FileScanner, MergeEngine, EditorHistoryExtractor classes\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"project-root-and-scripts\",\n    \"to_area\": \"web-templates\",\n    \"type\": \"configures\",\n    \"details\": \"CLAUDE.md references templates/ directory as part of project layout documentation\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"project-root-and-scripts\",\n    \"to_area\": \"claude-config-and-rules\",\n    \"type\": \"configures\",\n    \"details\": \"CLAUDE.md references .claude/rules/ as part of the rule discovery protocol\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"project-root-and-scripts\",\n    \"to_area\": \"agentic-docs-and-workflows\