e pagination with query parameter preservation\",\n        \"Sortable table headers with direction toggle\",\n        \"Filter tabs (All, Auto-merge, Conflicts, Unresolved)\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Tabular inventory view with pagination, sorting, filtering, and bulk action buttons for executing merges.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"templates/conflicts.html\",\n      \"role\": \"template\",\n      \"exports\": [\n        \"conflict list with progress bar\",\n        \"auto-resolve all button\",\n        \"completion detection\"\n      ],\n      \"imports_from\": [\n        \"base.html (extends)\",\n        \"Flask template variables: resolved, total, items\",\n        \"POST endpoint: /resolve-all-latest\",\n        \"GET endpoint: /conflict/*\"\n      ],\n      \"key_functions\": [],\n      \"patterns\": [\n        \"Progress visualization\",\n        \"Conditional completion UI\",\n        \"Quick navigation to individual conflict resolution\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Conflict resolution overview page showing progress, listing all conflicts with status, and providing bulk auto-resolution.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"templates/conflict_detail.html\",\n      \"role\": \"template\",\n      \"exports\": [\n        \"version comparison cards\",\n        \"side-by-side diff view\",\n        \"unified diff view\",\n        \"version selection form\",\n        \"keyboard shortcuts\"\n      ],\n      \"imports_from\": [\n        \"base.html (extends)\",\n        \"Flask template variables: filepath, prev_path, next_path, current_idx, total_conflicts, resolved, versions, diff_a_idx, diff_b_idx, side_by_side, diff_lines\",\n        \"POST endpoint: /resolve\",\n        \"GET endpoint: /merge/*\"\n      ],\n      \"key_functions\": [\n        \"switchDiffPair() - changes compared versions\",\n        \"selectVersion(idx) - selects a version visually\"\n      ],\n      \"patterns\": [\n        \"Tabbed interface for diff views\",\n        \"Previous/next navigation\",\n        \"Keyboard shortcuts (arrows, Enter, numbers, s/u for view toggle)\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Detailed conflict resolution page showing version metadata cards, selectable diff views, and version selection with navigation.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"templates/merge_editor.html\",\n      \"role\": \"template\",\n      \"exports\": [\n        \"interactive hunk-based merge editor\",\n        \"hunk picking (left/right/both/neither)\",\n        \"edit mode with text editor\",\n        \"live preview\",\n        \"keyboard shortcuts\"\n      ],\n      \"imports_from\": [\n        \"base.html (extends)\",\n        \"Flask template variables: filepath, versions, idx_a, idx_b, source_a, source_b, hunks\",\n        \"API endpoint: /api/save-merge\"\n      ],\n      \"key_functions\": [\n        \"pickHunk(id, side) - selects a side for a hunk\",\n        \"pickAllLeft()/pickAllRight() - bulk hunk selection\",\n        \"buildMergedContent() - constructs result from picks\",\n        \"toggleEditMode() - switches between hunk and text editor\",\n        \"saveMerge() - persists merged content\",\n        \"updateCounts() - tracks resolution progress\"\n      ],\n      \"patterns\": [\n        \"Hunk-based three-way merge UI\",\n        \"Dual-mode editing (hunk picker vs text editor)\",\n        \"Unsaved changes warning\",\n        \"Tab key handling in textarea\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Advanced merge editor allowing per-hunk resolution with visual diff, bulk actions, and manual text editing mode for fine-tuning results.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"templates/coverage.html\",\n      \"role\": \"template\",\n      \"exports\": [\n        \"source coverage visualization\",\n        \"progress bars per source\",\n        \"file categorization breakdown\",\n        \"lazy-loaded file lists\"\n      ],\n      \"imports_from\": [\n        \"base.html (extends)\",\n        \"Flask template variables: stats, coverage\",\n