 application. It implements a Bootstrap 5 dark-themed UI covering the full workflow: setup wizard with session management, interactive file browser with tree navigation and inline conflict resolution, inventory and conflict list views, advanced hunk-based merge editor, coverage dashboard, editor history extraction, and real-time progress pages using Server-Sent Events. The templates follow a consistent inheritance pattern from base.html, use AJAX extensively for dynamic content, and include rich client-side JavaScript for keyboard navigation, real-time updates, and interactive merge operations.\",\n  \"cross_area_refs\": [\n    \"imports get_flashed_messages, request from Flask (core-application)\",\n    \"imports API endpoints from core-application: /api/browse-tree, /api/file-detail/*, /api/file-content/*, /api/save-merge, /api/coverage-files/*\",\n    \"imports SSE endpoints from core-application: /scan-events, /merge-events, /extract-events\",\n    \"imports POST endpoints from core-application: /setup, /execute, /resolve, /resolve-toggle, /resolve-accept-defaults, /resolve-all-latest, /extract-history\",\n    \"imports GET endpoints from core-application: /browse, /inventory, /conflicts, /conflict/*, /merge/*, /coverage, /log, /setup, /extract-history, /export-log, /session/*\"\n  ],\n  \"suggested_splits\": []\n}\n```\n\n## Relationship Edges for This Area\n\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"web-templates\",\n    \"to_area\": \"core-application\",\n    \"type\": \"calls\",\n    \"details\": \"All templates consume Flask route endpoints: /api/browse-tree, /api/file-detail/*, /api/file-content/*, /api/save-merge, /api/coverage-files/*, /scan-events (SSE), /merge-events (SSE), /extract-events (SSE), /setup, /execute, /resolve, /resolve-toggle, /resolve-accept-defaults, /resolve-all-latest, /extract-history, /browse, /inventory, /conflicts, /conflict/*, /merge/*, /coverage, /log, /export-log, /session/*. Templates also use Flask context variables: get_flashed