lls (summaries), YAML frontmatter standard, and resolution pipeline.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"agentic/rules/docs/skills.md\",\n      \"role\": \"documentation\",\n      \"exports\": [],\n      \"imports_from\": [],\n      \"key_functions\": [],\n      \"patterns\": [\n        \"folder-based-config\",\n        \"yaml-frontmatter\",\n        \"sub-agent-pattern\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Skills architecture guide covering SKILL.md format, folder structure, JSON skill definitions, discovery mechanism, and sub-agent definitions.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"agentic/rules/docs/workflows.md\",\n      \"role\": \"documentation\",\n      \"exports\": [],\n      \"imports_from\": [],\n      \"key_functions\": [],\n      \"patterns\": [\n        \"execution-flow-docs\",\n        \"session-state-docs\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Workflow engine documentation covering LightweightWorkflowSession, layer processing pipeline, agentic loop modes (ReAct/native), and execution flow.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"agentic/skills/example-skill/SKILL.md\",\n      \"role\": \"template\",\n      \"exports\": [],\n      \"imports_from\": [],\n      \"key_functions\": [],\n      \"patterns\": [\n        \"yaml-frontmatter\",\n        \"phased-instructions\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Example skill template demonstrating the SKILL.md format with YAML frontmatter (name, description, allowed-tools) and phased instruction structure.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"agentic/workflows/example_workflow.json\",\n      \"role\": \"config\",\n      \"exports\": [],\n      \"imports_from\": [],\n      \"key_functions\": [],\n      \"patterns\": [\n        \"json-workflow-definition\",\n        \"jinja2-templating\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Example JSON workflow with two layers: an agentic_loop for file analysis and a smart_template for formatting output using Jinja2 variables.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"area_summary\": \"This area contains the complete documentation suite and templates for the agentic workflow engine. The documentation follows a self-contained design principle where each doc covers a specific concern (architecture, JSON definitions, knowledge system, skills, workflows) without requiring source code inspection. The area includes YAML-frontmatter-based skill templates and JSON workflow definitions that demonstrate the engine's capabilities. The architectural pattern is documentation-as-configuration: markdown files with structured frontmatter drive runtime behavior (skill discovery, knowledge injection) while serving as human-readable reference.\",\n  \"cross_area_refs\": [\n    \"references agentic.engine.run_workflow from agentic-engine\",\n    \"references agentic.engine.OpenRouterClient from agentic-engine\",\n    \"references agentic.tools.read_file from agentic-tools\",\n    \"references agentic.tools.search_code from agentic-tools\",\n    \"references agentic.tools.list_directory from agentic-tools\",\n    \"references agentic.tools.write_file from agentic-tools\",\n    \"references agentic.tools.get_file_tree from agentic-tools\",\n    \"references agentic.engine.knowledge.resolve_knowledge from agentic-engine\",\n    \"references agentic.engine.knowledge.discover_skills from agentic-engine\",\n    \"references agentic.engine.runner.LightweightWorkflowSession from agentic-engine\",\n    \"references agentic.tools.definitions.json from agentic-tools\"\n  ],\n  \"suggested_splits\": []\n}\n```\n\n## Relationship Edges for This Area\n\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"project-root-and-scripts\",\n    \"to_area\": \"agentic-docs-and-workflows\",\n    \"type\": \"configures\",\n    \"details\": \"CLAUDE.md references agentic/ documentation as part of the project documentation index\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"agentic-docs-and-workflows\",\n    \"to_area\": \"agentic-engine\",\n    \"type\": \"shares_types\",\n    \"details\": \"Documentation references: agentic.engine.run_workflow, agentic.engine.OpenRouterClient, agentic.engine.knowledge.resolve_knowledge, agentic.engine.knowledge.discover_skills, agentic.engine.runner.LightweightWorkflowSession\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"agentic-docs-and-workflows\",\n    \"to_area\": \"agentic-tools\",\n    \"type\": \"shares_types\",\n    \"details\": \"Documentation references: agentic.tools.read_file, agentic.tools.search_code, agentic.tools.list_directory, agentic.tools.write_file, agentic.tools.get_file_tree, agentic.tools.definitions.json\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n## Repo Analysis (AST-based)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"repo\": \"local/Guanine(CodeEdit)-9b8e0840\",\n  \"indexed_at\": \"2026-04-06T16:32:22.900574\",\n  \"file_count\": 39,\n  \"symbol_count\": 519,\n  \"languages\": {\n    \"python\": 39\n  },\n  \"directories\": {\n    \".code-index/\": 26,\n    \"agentic/\": 12,\n    \"(root)\": 1\n  },\n  \"symbol_kinds\": {\n    \"function\": 297,\n    \"method\": 147,\n    \"constant\": 45,\n    \"class\": 30\n  },\n  \"most_central_symbols\": [\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/engine/knowledge.py::resolve_knowledge#function\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"function\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/engine/loop.py::process_agentic_loop#function\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"function\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/engine/openrouter.py::OpenRouterClient#class\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"class\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/engine/runner.py::LightweightWorkflowSession#class\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"class\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/engine/tool_executor.py::execute_tool_call#function\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"function\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/tools/get_file_tree.py::_build_tree#function\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"function\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/tools/list_directory.py::_list_entries#function\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"function\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"symbol_id\": \".code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/.code-index/local-Guanine-CodeEdit-9b8e0840/agentic/tools/read_file.py::execute#function\",\n      \"score\": 0.025641,\n      \"kind\": \"function\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"_meta\": {\n    \"timing_ms\": 18.6,\n    \"tokens_saved\": 124632,\n    \"total_tokens_saved\": 410029,\n    \"is_stale\": null\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Instructions\n\nWrite the documentation file to `.claude/rules/docs/agentic-docs-and-workflows.md` following the document template in your system prompt. Use `write_file` to create the file. Then update the rules index using `update_rules_index` with:\n- index_path: `.claude/rules/RULES_INDEX.md`\n- entry_path: `docs/agentic-docs-and-workflows.md`\n- summary: A one-line summary of this area\n- section: `Documentation Rules`"
