ss_layer`, and all layer processors.\\n- **Downstream `agentic-tools`** must maintain callable signatures compatible with `_filter_args` introspection (standard `inspect.Parameter` patterns).\\n- **`agentic-docs-and-workflows`** references this area's public API surface; signature changes should be documented there.\\n\\n## Change History\\n> Initial documentation generated by Spark.\\n\",\"kwargs\":\"{}\"}"
