c_loop(layer_def, session, client, tool_registry, knowledge) -> dict\",\n        \"process_agentic_loop_native(layer_def, session, client, tool_registry, knowledge) -> dict\",\n        \"summarize_loop(chat_history, client, model) -> str\",\n        \"_build_system_message(layer_def, knowledge, tool_descriptions, mode) -> str\",\n        \"_tool_descriptions_text(tool_registry) -> str\",\n        \"_tool_schemas(tool_registry) -> list[dict]\",\n        \"_safe_summarize(chat_history, client, model) -> str\",\n        \"_format_transcript(messages) -> str\"\n      ],\n      \"imports_from\": [\n        \"execute_tool_call from .tool_executor\",\n        \"json (stdlib)\",\n        \"logging (stdlib)\",\n        \"re (stdlib)\",\n        \"typing.Any (stdlib)\"\n      ],\n      \"key_functions\": [\n        \"process_agentic_loop(layer_def, session, client, tool_registry, knowledge) -> dict \\u2014 ReAct-style text-parsed agentic loop with Thought/Action/Answer format\",\n        \"process_agentic_loop_native(layer_def, session, client, tool_registry, knowledge) -> dict \\u2014 Native OpenAI-format function calling agentic loop\",\n        \"summarize_loop(chat_history, client, model) -> str \\u2014 Generates structured summary of agent conversation covering objective, actions, result, and artifacts\",\n        \"_build_system_message(layer_def, knowledge, tool_descriptions, mode) -> str \\u2014 Assembles complete system prompt from layer definition, rules, skills, and tool descriptions\",\n        \"_tool_schemas(tool_registry) -> list[dict] \\u2014 Auto-generates OpenAI-format tool schemas from function signatures with tool_schema attribute support\"\n      ],\n      \"patterns\": [\n        \"ReAct pattern (Reasoning + Acting)\",\n        \"Strategy pattern (react vs native modes)\",\n        \"Template method pattern for system message assembly\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Implements dual-mode agentic loops: ReAct text-parsing and native tool-calling, with shared system message assembly and automatic conversation summarization.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"agentic/engine/openrouter.py\",\n      \"role\": \"service\",\n      \"exports\": [\n        \"OpenRouterClient\",\n        \"OpenRouterError\",\n        \"_MAX_RETRIES\",\n        \"_BACKOFF_SECONDS\"\n      ],\n      \"imports_from\": [\n        \"json (stdlib)\",\n        \"logging (stdlib)\",\n        \"time (stdlib)\",\n        \"urllib.error (stdlib)\",\n        \"urllib.request (stdlib)\",\n        \"typing.Any (stdlib)\"\n      ],\n      \"key_functions\": [\n        \"OpenRouterClient.__init__(api_key, base_url) \\u2014 Initializes client with API credentials\",\n        \"OpenRouterClient.chat_completion(model, messages, tools, max_tokens, temperature, stop) -> dict \\u2014 Sends chat completion request with retry logic and returns normalized response\",\n        \"OpenRouterClient._post(path, payload) -> dict \\u2014 Internal POST with exponential backoff retry for 429/5xx errors\",\n        \"OpenRouterClient._normalise(raw) -> dict \\u2014 Extracts first choice into flat dict with content, tool_calls, and usage keys\"\n      ],\n      \"patterns\": [\n        \"Retry pattern with exponential backoff\",\n        \"Adapter pattern (normalizes OpenRouter API responses)\",\n        \"Circuit breaker pattern (distinguishes retryable vs non-retryable errors)\"\n      ],\n      \"summary\": \"Lightweight stdlib-only HTTP client for OpenRouter API with automatic retry, exponential backoff, and normalized response format.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"agentic/engine/runner.py\",\n      \"role\": \"controller\",\n      \"exports\": [\n        \"LightweightWorkflowSession\",\n        \"process_layer(layer_def, session, client, tool_registry) -> dict\",\n        \"run_workflow(workflow_json, client, tool_registry, input_data) -> dict\",\n        \"_resolve_placeholders(text, session) -> str\",\n        \"_render_jinja(template_str, context) -> str\",\n  