onomous AI workflow engine implementing a layered architecture for LLM-powered automation. It provides a multi-layer workflow runner (runner.py) that orchestrates sequential processing steps, dual-mode agentic loops (loop.py) supporting both ReAct text-parsing and native OpenAI function-calling patterns, a stdlib-only OpenRouter HTTP client (openrouter.py) with retry logic, safe tool execution (tool_executor.py) with signature filtering, and a knowledge resolution system (knowledge.py) for discovering and assembling rules/skills into prompts. The engine uses Jinja2 templating, session-based state management, and XML-wrapped knowledge injection to create flexible, composable AI workflows without external dependencies beyond jinja2.\",\n  \"cross_area_refs\": [\n    \"imports jinja2 from external package (runner.py)\",\n    \"imports execute_tool_call from tool_executor (loop.py)\",\n    \"imports OpenRouterClient from openrouter (runner.py, loop.py)\",\n    \"imports process_agentic_loop, process_agentic_loop_native from loop (runner.py)\",\n    \"imports resolve_knowledge from knowledge (runner.py)\"\n  ],\n  \"suggested_splits\": []\n}\n```\n\n## Relationship Edges for This Area\n\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"agentic-engine\",\n    \"to_area\": \"agentic-tools\",\n    \"type\": \"calls\",\n    \"details\": \"tool_executor.py dispatches tool calls to tool execute() functions; runner.py passes tool_registry containing agentic-tools modules; loop.py invokes execute_tool_call which calls into tool modules\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"agentic-docs-and-workflows\",\n    \"to_area\": \"agentic-engine\",\n    \"type\": \"shares_types\",\n    \"details\": \"Documentation references: agentic.engine.run_workflow, agentic.engine.OpenRouterClient, agentic.engine.knowledge.resolve_knowledge, agentic.engine.knowledge.discover_skills, agentic.engine.runner.LightweightWorkflowSession\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"from_area\": \"agentic-engine\",\n    \"to_area\": \"agentic-engine\",\n    \"type\": \"imports\",\n    \"details\": \"Internal cross-module imports: __init__.py re-exports from all submodules; runner.py imports OpenRouterClient from openrouter, process_agentic_loop/process_agentic_loop_native from loop, resolve_knowledge from knowledge; loop.py imports execute_tool_call from tool_executor\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n## Shared Types Involving This Area\n\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"name\": \"OpenRouterClient\",\n    \"defined_in\": \"agentic-engine\",\n    \"used_in\": [\n      \"agentic-engine\",\n      \"agentic-docs-and-workflows\"\n    ],\n    \"description\": \"HTTP client for OpenRouter LLM API. Defined in openrouter.py, used by runner.py and loop.py, documented in agentic docs.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"LightweightWorkflowSession\",\n    \"defined_in\": \"agentic-engine\",\n    \"used_in\": [\n      \"agentic-engine\",\n      \"agentic-docs-and-workflows\"\n    ],\n    \"description\": \"Session state container for workflow execution. Defined in runner.py, referenced in workflow documentation.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Knowledge resolution types (rules, skills, knowledge_set)\",\n    \"defined_in\": \"agentic-engine\",\n    \"used_in\": [\n      \"agentic-engine\",\n      \"agentic-docs-and-workflows\"\n    ],\n    \"description\": \"Knowledge system concepts: resolve_knowledge(), discover_skills(), build_rules_index(), build_skills_index(), extract_frontmatter(). Defined in knowledge.py, consumed by runner.py, documented in knowledge-system.md and skills.md.\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n## Repo Analysis (AST-based)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"repo\": \"local/Guanine(CodeEdit)-9b8e0840\",\n  \"indexed_at\": \"2026-04-06T16:32:22.900574\",\n  \"file_count\": 39,\n  \"symbol_count\": 519,\n  \"languages\": {\n    \"python\": 39\n  },\n  \"directories\": {\n    \".code-index/\": 26,\n    \"agentic/\": 12,\n    \"(root)\": 1\n  },\n  \"symbol_kinds\": {\n    \"function\": 297,\n    \"method\": 147,\n    \"constant\": 45,\n    \"class\": 30\n  },\n  \